flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Periodic review of supply chain costs and performance metrics.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest vehicle line costs from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze vehicle line costs using TCO models.]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: AutoML - Develop should-cost targets and negotiation strategies.]
  N3 --> N4{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Lead VA/VE initiatives to propose cost-reduction and performance improvements.}
  N4 -->|Primary| N5[Cortex: RCA Service - Identify key cost drivers in commodities.]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Remote Functions - Implement selected strategies and monitor outcomes.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Measurable reductions in material costs, manufacturing costs, and supplier terms while maintaining or improving product quality and delivery performance.]
  N4 -->|High variance in component costs.| B1[Adjust should-cost targets and re-evaluate negotiation strategies.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Improved cost alignment and negotiation leverage.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Significant VA/VE proposal rejected.| B2[Review and adjust VA/VE proposals based on feedback.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Enhanced proposal acceptance rate and cost reduction.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Unfavorable commodity market trends.| B3[Implement hedging and supplier diversification strategies.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Reduced exposure to market volatility and improved profitability.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]